		<title>04Steetley Quarry</title>
		<content> The manufacture of lime is carried    
 out in vertical shafts, rotary or     
 rotary hearth kilns. When burning     
 conditions are severe and where fire  
 alumina bricks do not give a          
 satisfactory performance, Steetley    
 recommends the use of high fired, high
 hot strength abrasion resistant basic 
 bricks. These bricks are used in      
 Steetley's own lime burning kilns.    
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
